title.rendered: RVDK Ronald van der Kemp. SS 2023 Haute Couture Week.

content.rendered:
RVDK Ronald van der Kemp. Spring-Summer 2023 Couture Collection during Haute Couture Week.

Wardrobe 17

Todays happening is an invitation for dialogue Its about realness, self expression and new ideas A chance to change and opening up our minds

Cant you feel a brand new day?

Collection


Text and Photo: Press Ronald van der Kemp.

More on: www.ronaldvanderkemp.com @ronaldvanderkemp

Thanks: Lucien Pages @lucienpagescommunication


By Senior Fashion Editor 24FashionTV: Christina V Henningstad @christina_henningstad
